{"tid":1570432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾國斌：美國國會議員不希望介入香港事務","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:04:36.000Z","uid":225818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69e11d77b7f2af3720f0c9f2f6f5f81337d40bcc","tid":1570432,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國國會將審議《香港人權與民主法案》，自由黨黨魁鍾國斌在本台節目《大鳴大放》中，引述部分當地國會議員指，並不希望處理香港問題，擔心若美方介入只會惡化局勢。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌又認為即使法案獲通過，對商界不會有太大影響。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府月初宣布撤回修例，鍾國斌認為已是太遲，但總比堅持不撤回好，他相信如短期內可平息動盪，香港經濟可於短期內反彈<br />\n<br />\nSource : NOW新聞 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=37d77f68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&h=94eae1a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚驚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又對美國內政說三道四<br />\n一齊上twitter話比美國國會議員聽佢地被代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備同毒瘤一齊被點名制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw呢個法案又唔係針對制裁商人<br />\n對商界影響不大唔係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a809c0be2535c51d344d4f4f35d01d0465800b","tid":1570432,"uid":254551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"無影響咪通過囉做乜啫"}]}